Seadrill to Sell 25% of North Atlantic Drilling Unit

-- B y   J o n a s   B e r g m a n
-- 
2011-02-15T09:41:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/seadrill-to-sell-25-of-north-atlantic-drilling-unit-correct-.html
(Corrects million to billion shares in second paragraph.)    Seadrill Ltd . said it expects gross
proceeds of $1.7 billion in a private placement of new shares in
North Atlantic Drilling Ltd.  Seadrill said it will subscribe to 75 percent of the
offering of 1 billion shares at $1.7 a piece. The transaction
will start today and close on Feb. 16. Seadrill said it expects
to apply for a listing on the Oslo Stock Exchange this year.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
